ModMetadata.Description:
[h1]IC10OCD[/h1]
    This is a Plugin Mod. 
	  It requires Bepinex to be installed with the StationeersLaunchPad plugin.
	  See: https://github.com/StationeersLaunchPad/StationeersLaunchPad 
	  [img]https://i.imgur.com/c3qYm69.png[/img]

        This mod runs a Httplistener along side the game providing a few endpoints to retrive information on the ic10 chips present in the game.

        GET endpoints:
        "list-chips"
        "chip-info/{refid}":
        "chip-dump/{refid}":
        "chip-code/{refid}":
        "chip-network-device-list/{refid}":
        "chip-mem/{refid}/{register | stack}/{addr}":

        POST endpoints:
        "chip-dump/{refid}"
        "chip-code/{refid}"
        "toggle-chip-power/{refid}"
        "chip-mem/{refid}/{register | stack}/{addr}"

        [b]Schemas:[/b]
        chip-info
        {
            string name;
            string refid;
            string holder_name;
            string holder_refid;
            string compileErrorLineNumber;
            string compileErrorType;
            bool on;
        }

        network-device-info
        {
            string name;
            string refid;
            string uplink;
        }

        chip-code
        {
            string code;
        }

        chip-dump
        {
            number[] registers;
            number[] stack;
            number? lineNumber;
        }

        chip-mem-value 
        {
            number value;
        }

    GitHub: https://github.com/vespinian/ic10ocd
